data.text:
Love Emmerdale? Check out this complete Emmerdale cast list, including photos of the actors when available. This list includes all of the Emmerdale main actors and actresses, so if they are an integral part of the show, you'll find them below. You can find various bits of trivia about these Emmerdale stars, such as where the actor was born and what their year of birth is. This cast list of actors from Emmerdale focuses primarily on the main characters, but there may be a few actors who played smaller roles on Emmerdale that are on here as well.

Items on this poll include Jeff Hordley and Eden Taylor-Draper, among a range of actors and actresses from past seasons. If you are wondering, "Who are the actors from Emmerdale?" or "Who starred on Emmerdale?" then this list will help you answer those questions. You can also go vote for the best actors on Emmerdale.

In most cases you can click on the names of these popular Emmerdale actors and actresses to find out more information about them. If you're looking for a particular Emmerdale actor or actress, then type their name into the "search" bar to find them directly.
